        "creation_date": 1616705101,
        "body": "<p>Looking at the <a href=\"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-data-mongodb/blob/6d662461b89589a8485e4ae3ec37e8bd42c5c500/spring-data-mongodb/src/main/java/org/springframework/data/mongodb/core/convert/MongoConverters.java#L202\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">source code<\/a>, that simply is what Spring decides to use as a representation.\nThe underlying problem is that there is no valid numeric <a href=\"https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/reference/bson-types/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">MongoDB datatype<\/a> that can be used to reliably represent all possible values of BigInteger.<\/p>\n",
